query:
SELECT 
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM products) as total_products,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM product_categories) as total_associations,
  (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT brand) FROM products) as total_brands,
  (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT productType) FROM products WHERE productType IS NOT NULL) as total_types
